ies\nthat can maintain a uniform distribution of power consumption by aggregated\nheterogeneous loads will enable distribution system management (DSM) approaches\nthat maintain stability as well as power quality, and further allow more\nintegration of renewable energy sources.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 9 Mar 2018 04:17:14 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-03-12"}
