 in\nnetwork jets should not be taken as real mass upflows but only as apparent\nspeeds of a rapidly propagating heating front along the pre-existing spicule.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 9 Mar 2018 07:43:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-05-02"}
